{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "TCC 协调服务 API (app_tcc)",
    "description": "分布式 TCC 全局事务协调：Try / Confirm / Cancel 阶段编排与查询。仅在 `APP_TCC_ENABLED=true` 时挂载；HTTP 前缀：`/api/tcc/`（见 `service_foundation/urls.py` → `app_tcc/urls.py`）。\n\n**响应包络**：`{ errorCode, data, message, ... }`。`errorCode === 0`（`RET_OK`）表示成功；参数与业务错误通常仍返回 **HTTP 200**，以 `errorCode` 区分。\n\n**成功响应**：`resp_ok` 会设置 `Expires` 响应头（约 5 秒后过期）。\n\n**鉴权**：当前业务视图 `authentication_classes = []`，无会话/Token 校验（若网关层有鉴权需单独配置）。\n\n**XXL-JOB 执行器**（`/api/tcc/xxl-job/*`）：响应为 `{ code, msg, data }`（`code` 为 200/500），与业务 API 包络**不同**；请求头 `XXL-JOB-ACCESS-TOKEN`（与 `XXL_JOB_TOKEN` 一致），配置见 `XXL_JOB_*`（与 `app_saga` 共用 `common` 内执行器）。内建任务名 **`tccScan`**：同步执行与 `python manage.py tcc_scan` 相同逻辑（`executorParams` 可选为 batch `limit`）。\n\n**状态码（整数）**：全局事务见 `GlobalTxStatus`（INIT=10, TRYING=20, AWAIT_CONFIRM=30, CONFIRMING=40, CANCELING=50, COMMITTED=60, ROLLED_BACK=70, NEEDS_MANUAL=80）；分支见 `BranchStatus`（PENDING_TRY=10, TRY_SUCCEEDED=20, TRY_FAILED=30, CONFIRM_SUCCEEDED=40, CONFIRM_FAILED=50, CANCEL_SUCCEEDED=60, CANCEL_FAILED=70），定义于 `app_tcc/enums.py`。",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "/",
      "description": "相对当前站点根路径"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "description": "存活检查"
    },
    {
      "name": "Transactions",
      "description": "全局事务：开启、查询、确认、取消"
    },
    {
      "name": "XXL-JOB",
      "description": "XXL-JOB 嵌入式执行器（与 `app_saga` 同实现、注册名不同）"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/api/tcc/health": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Health"],
        "summary": "健康检查",
        "description": "返回固定负载，表示 TCC 应用路由已启用。",
        "operationId": "tccHealth",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功（`errorCode=0`）",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "allOf": [
                        { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeOk" },
                        {
                          "type": "object",
                          "properties": {
                            "data": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TccHealthPayload" }
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeError" }
                  ]
                },
                "examples": {
                  "success": {
                    "summary": "成功",
                    "value": {
                      "errorCode": 0,
                      "message": "",
                      "data": { "status": "ok", "service": "tcc" }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {
              "Expires": {
                "description": "成功时由 `resp_ok` 设置",
                "schema": { "type": "string" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/tcc/tx": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Transactions"],
        "summary": "开启全局事务（Try 阶段及后续）",
        "description": "请求体为 **二选一**。\n\n**A. 经典** — 根上 `biz_id` + `branches` 等，见 `TccBeginRequest`。\n\n**B. Saga 外呼** — 有 `saga_instance_id` 与 **`payload`（object）** 时解析为 begin：`biz_id` ← **`payload.biz_id`**（int，正，必填）；`branches` 等在 **`payload`** 内。`tcc_access_key` 可在 **`saga_shared`** 或根上重复（可忽略）。Saga 编排器外呼**仅**在 `saga_shared` 中携带 `step_payloads` 与可选 `tcc_access_key`；根级 `flow_id` 为 Saga 流程 ID，**不是** TCC `biz_id`。\n\n**响应 `data.branches`（A/B 相同）**：为以各分支的 **`branch_code`**（与 `TccBranchMeta.code`、begin 入参 `branches[].branch_code` 相同）为键的对象（**禁止**缺 `branch_meta.code` 时用其他占位键；未配置时在查询/列详情会 `errorCode=100`）。值为 `TccBranchSummary`（内含 `branch_code` 字段；`data` 为参与者最近一次成功 HTTP 的 JSON 体，解析结果或 `null`）。\n\n**错误**：非法 JSON/缺字段/类型错误 → `errorCode=100`（`RET_INVALID_PARAM`）；Snowflake 分配失败 → `100`；未捕获异常 → `errorCode=-1`（`resp_exception`）。",
        "operationId": "tccTxBegin",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "oneOf": [
                  { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TccBeginRequest" },
                  { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SagaTccTxCallback" }
                ]
              },
              "examples": {
                "classic": {
                  "summary": "经典直连",
                  "value": {
                    "biz_id": 1,
                    "branches": [{ "branch_code": "pay", "payload": { "order_id": "a1" } }],
                    "auto_confirm": false,
                    "context": { "biz": "demo" }
                  }
                },
                "fromSaga": {
                  "summary": "Saga 步骤外呼（`biz_id` 在 `payload`，与编排器 `saga_shared` 一致）",
                  "value": {
                    "saga_instance_id": "1001",
                    "idem_key": 9876543210987654321,
                    "flow_id": 5,
                    "step_index": 0,
                    "phase": "action",
                    "context": {},
                    "saga_shared": {
                      "tcc_access_key": "tcc-access-or-jwt",
                      "step_payloads": { "pay": {} }
                    },
                    "payload": {
                      "biz_id": 10,
                      "branches": [{ "branch_code": "pay", "payload": { "order_id": "a1" } }],
                      "auto_confirm": false,
                      "context": { "biz": "demo" }
                    },
                    "start_request": { "flow_id": 5, "access_key": "saga-key" }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功（`errorCode=0`，`data` 为事务详情）或参数/依赖错误（`errorCode≠0`，HTTP 仍为 200）",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "allOf": [
                        { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeOk" },
                        {
                          "type": "object",
                          "properties": {
                            "data": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TccTransactionDetail" }
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeError" }
                  ]
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {
              "Expires": {
                "description": "成功时由 `resp_ok` 设置",
                "schema": { "type": "string" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/tcc/tx/{idem_key}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Transactions"],
        "summary": "查询全局事务详情",
        "description": "路径参数 `idem_key` 为 `TccGlobalTransaction.idem_key`（开启事务响应体中的 `idem_key` 字段）的十进制字符串，前后空白会被 trim。空字符串或非十进制整数 → `errorCode=100`（`idem_key required` / `idem_key must be a decimal integer string`）；找不到事务 → `100`（`transaction not found`）。成功时 `data` 结构与 `serialize_transaction` 一致（仍含 `global_tx_id` 主键与 `idem_key`）。",
        "operationId": "tccTxDetail",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "idem_key",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "全局事务幂等键（`idem_key`，与 `POST /api/tcc/tx` 成功响应中字段一致）。",
            "schema": { "type": "string", "pattern": "^[0-9]+$", "example": "9876543210987654321" }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功或业务错误（HTTP 200）",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "allOf": [
                        { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeOk" },
                        {
                          "type": "object",
                          "properties": {
                            "data": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TccTransactionDetail" }
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeError" }
                  ]
                },
                "examples": {
                  "notFound": {
                    "summary": "未找到事务",
                    "value": {
                      "errorCode": 100,
                      "message": "transaction not found",
                      "data": null
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {
              "Expires": {
                "description": "成功时由 `resp_ok` 设置",
                "schema": { "type": "string" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/tcc/tx/{idem_key}/confirm": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Transactions"],
        "summary": "确认全局事务（进入 Confirm 阶段）",
        "description": "路径参数 `idem_key` 同「查询详情」接口。仅当当前状态为 **`AWAIT_CONFIRM`** 时可确认；否则 `errorCode=100`。路径格式非法时同详情接口。成功返回更新后的 `TccTransactionDetail`。未捕获异常 → `errorCode=-1`。",
        "operationId": "tccTxConfirm",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "idem_key",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "全局事务幂等键（与 `POST /api/tcc/tx` 响应中 `idem_key` 一致）。",
            "schema": { "type": "string", "example": "9876543210987654321" }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功或错误（HTTP 200）",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "allOf": [
                        { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeOk" },
                        {
                          "type": "object",
                          "properties": {
                            "data": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TccTransactionDetail" }
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeError" }
                  ]
                },
                "examples": {
                  "invalidState": {
                    "summary": "非待确认状态",
                    "value": {
                      "errorCode": 100,
                      "message": "transaction is not awaiting confirm",
                      "data": null
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {
              "Expires": {
                "description": "成功时由 `resp_ok` 设置",
                "schema": { "type": "string" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/tcc/tx/{idem_key}/cancel": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Transactions"],
        "summary": "取消全局事务（进入 Cancel 阶段）",
        "description": "路径参数 `idem_key` 同「查询详情」接口。请求体为 JSON 对象；**`cancel_reason` 可选**，省略时按 **`UNPAID`（0）** 处理（与 `app_tcc.enums.CancelReason` 一致）。对已 **COMMITTED**、**ROLLED_BACK** 或 **NEEDS_MANUAL** 的事务调用会返回 `errorCode=100`（`transaction is already terminal`）。对其余非终态事务置为取消阶段并对已成功 Try 的分支逆序调用 Cancel；参与者 `cancel_url` 的 JSON 体会带 `cancel_reason` 与 `last_cancel_reason` 一致。Try 失败或待确认超时等由协调器触发的取消使用内部原因（见 `CancelReason`）。成功返回 `TccTransactionDetail`。未捕获异常 → `errorCode=-1`。",
        "operationId": "tccTxCancel",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "idem_key",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "全局事务幂等键（与 `POST /api/tcc/tx` 响应中 `idem_key` 一致）。",
            "schema": { "type": "string", "example": "9876543210987654321" }
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TccCancelRequest" },
              "example": { "cancel_reason": 0 }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "成功或错误（HTTP 200）",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "oneOf": [
                    {
                      "allOf": [
                        { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeOk" },
                        {
                          "type": "object",
                          "properties": {
                            "data": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TccTransactionDetail" }
                          }
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/EnvelopeError" }
                  ]
                }
              }
            },
            "headers": {
              "Expires": {
                "description": "成功时由 `resp_ok` 设置",
                "schema": { "type": "string" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/tcc/xxl-job/beat": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["XXL-JOB"],
        "summary": "XXL-JOB 执行器心跳",
        "description": "同 `/api/saga/xxl-job/beat`；`XXL-JOB-ACCESS-TOKEN` 与 `XXL_JOB_TOKEN` 一致。",
        "operationId": "tccXxlBeat",
        "security": [{ "XxlJobAccessToken": [] }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/XxlJobExecutorResponse" }
              }
            },
            "description": ""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/tcc/xxl-job/run": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["XXL-JOB"],
        "summary": "执行一次任务（同步）",
        "description": "同 Saga 端 `/run` 契约；本应用预注册 `tccScan`（`python manage.py tcc_scan` 等价）。**必填**：`jobId`、`logId`、`executorHandler`。",
        "operationId": "tccXxlRun",
        "security": [{ "XxlJobAccessToken": [] }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/XxlJobRunBody" }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/XxlJobExecutorResponse" }
              }
            },
            "description": ""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/tcc/xxl-job/kill": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["XXL-JOB"],
        "summary": "kill（无操作）",
        "description": "同步执行器占位返回 noop。",
        "operationId": "tccXxlKill",
        "security": [{ "XxlJobAccessToken": [] }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/XxlJobExecutorResponse" }
              }
            },
            "description": ""
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "XxlJobAccessToken": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "in": "header",
        "name": "XXL-JOB-ACCESS-TOKEN"
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "XxlJobExecutorResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["code", "msg"],
        "properties": {
          "code": { "type": "integer", "enum": [200, 500] },
          "msg": { "type": "string" },
          "data": { "nullable": true }
        }
      },
      "XxlJobRunBody": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["jobId", "logId", "executorHandler"],
        "properties": {
          "jobId": { "type": "integer" },
          "logId": { "type": "integer" },
          "executorHandler": { "type": "string" },
          "executorParams": { "type": "string", "nullable": true }
        }
      },
      "EnvelopeOk": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["errorCode", "message"],
        "properties": {
          "errorCode": {
            "type": "integer",
            "enum": [0],
            "description": "成功为 0（RET_OK）"
          },
          "data": { "description": "业务数据" },
          "message": { "type": "string", "description": "成功时通常为空串" }
        }
      },
      "EnvelopeError": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["errorCode", "message"],
        "properties": {
          "errorCode": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "非 0。常见：`100`（RET_INVALID_PARAM）；`-1` 未捕获异常（resp_exception）"
          },
          "data": { "nullable": true },
          "message": { "type": "string" },
          "detail": { "type": "string" },
          "_req_id": { "type": "string" }
        }
      },
      "TccHealthPayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["status", "service"],
        "properties": {
          "status": { "type": "string", "enum": ["ok"] },
          "service": { "type": "string", "enum": ["tcc"] }
        }
      },
      "SagaTccTxCallback": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "当 `saga_instance_id` 与 `payload` 同时存在时：``biz_id`` ← **`payload.biz_id`**（正 int，必填）；``branch_items`` ← `payload.branches`；`saga_shared` 含 `step_payloads` 与可选 `tcc_access_key`（编排器不将 TCC `biz_id` 放在 `saga_shared`）",
        "required": ["saga_instance_id", "payload"],
        "properties": {
          "saga_instance_id": { "type": "string", "description": "Saga 实例主键（字符串）" },
          "idem_key": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64" },
          "flow_id": { "type": "integer", "description": "Saga 流程 ID（非 TCC `biz_id`）" },
          "saga_shared": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "须含 `step_payloads`；`tcc_access_key` 可选。TCC `biz_id` 在 **`payload.biz_id`**，不在此对象内"
          },
          "payload": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "须含 `biz_id`（正 int，TCC 即 `TccBizMeta.id`）、`branches`（array，必非空）；可选 `auto_confirm`、`context`",
            "additionalProperties": true
          },
          "phase": { "type": "string" },
          "context": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": true },
          "start_request": { "type": "object", "additionalProperties": true }
        }
      },
      "TccBeginBranchItem": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["branch_code"],
        "properties": {
          "branch_code": {
            "type": "string",
            "minLength": 1,
            "maxLength": 64,
            "description": "与 `TccBranchMeta.code` 一致，同一 `biz_id` 下唯一；begin 请求内不可重复；strip 后非空"
          },
          "payload": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": true,
            "description": "可选；省略等价于 `{}`。若非对象则返回参数错误"
          }
        }
      },
      "TccCancelReason": {
        "type": "integer",
        "description": "业务取消原因；定义于 `app_tcc.enums.CancelReason`",
        "enum": [0, 10, 20],
        "x-enum-varnames": ["UNPAID", "ORDER_CLOSED", "DUPLICATE_CALLBACK"]
      },
      "TccCancelRequest": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "可传空对象 `{}`；`cancel_reason` 省略时服务端使用 `UNPAID`（0）。",
        "properties": {
          "cancel_reason": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TccCancelReason" }
        }
      },
      "TccBeginRequest": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["biz_id", "branches"],
        "properties": {
          "biz_id": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "业务元数据主键（`TccBizMeta.id` / `biz_meta.id`）"
          },
          "branches": {
            "type": "array",
            "minItems": 1,
            "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TccBeginBranchItem" }
          },
          "auto_confirm": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "description": "省略时使用服务端默认 `TCC_DEFAULT_AUTO_CONFIRM`"
          },
          "context": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": true,
            "description": "可选全局上下文对象"
          }
        }
      },
      "TccBranchSummary": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "tx_branch_id",
          "branch_meta_id",
          "branch_index",
          "branch_code",
          "branch_status",
          "last_http_status",
          "last_error",
          "data"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "tx_branch_id": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "description": "`tx_branch` 表主键（`TccBranch.id` / `pk`），与库中 bigint 一致"
          },
          "branch_meta_id": { "type": "integer" },
          "branch_index": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 0 },
          "branch_code": {
            "type": "string",
            "minLength": 1,
            "description": "与 `TccBranchMeta.code` 相同；`data.branches` 的**对象键**即该值（与 begin 入参 `branches[].branch_code` 对应）"
          },
          "branch_status": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "分支状态，见 `BranchStatus`（10–70）"
          },
          "last_http_status": {
            "type": "integer",
            "nullable": true,
            "description": "最后一次调用参与者 HTTP 状态码；无则为 null"
          },
          "last_error": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "错误信息截断至约 200 字符"
          },
          "data": {
            "description": "参与者返回体 JSON（最近一次成功 2xx 时解析；空体或非 JSON 为 null）",
            "nullable": true
          }
        }
      },
      "TccTransactionDetail": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "global_tx_id",
          "idem_key",
          "status",
          "auto_confirm",
          "retry_count",
          "branches"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "global_tx_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "全局事务主键的字符串形式"
          },
          "idem_key": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "description": "开启时分配的 Snowflake 幂等键"
          },
          "status": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "全局状态，见 `GlobalTxStatus`（10–80）"
          },
          "auto_confirm": { "type": "boolean" },
          "retry_count": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 0 },
          "branches": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "按 `branch_code` 为键的映射（与 begin 的 `branches[].branch_code` 及元数据 `TccBranchMeta.code` 对齐）",
            "additionalProperties": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TccBranchSummary" }
          },
          "review_snapshot": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "当存在人工复核记录时存在；为 `TccManualReview.snapshot` 文本（通常为 JSON 字符串）"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
